- Share the source code with proper attribution (link to the original repository)

### You CANNOT:

- Sell, sublicense, or commercially distribute the source code or any derivative work without explicit written permission from the author
- Redistribute the source code or compiled builds as a paid product, template, SaaS offering, or commercial service
- Remove or alter any credits, attributions, or license notices
- Claim this work as your own
- Use the source code to create a competing commercial product

