## 2. Pre-built APK License (Paid)

The official pre-built, signed APK of KiranaMitra is available for purchase at **₹999 INR (one-time payment)** from the official website or authorized distribution channels.

### Purchasers receive:

- A ready-to-use signed APK with all features
- Lifetime access to future updates at no additional cost
- Email support from the developer

### Terms:

- The APK is licensed to the individual purchaser for personal or business use (e.g., managing their kirana store)
- The APK must not be redistributed, resold, shared publicly, or reverse-engineered for commercial purposes
- One purchase covers usage on the purchaser's own devices

